'''Philip Glass''' l'est né au 31 ed jinvié 1937 à Baltimore dins l'étot du [[Maryland]]. Ch' est un musichien et pi un compositeu [[Étots-Unis|améritchin]] ed musike contimporaine. Il est considéré conme un compositeu très influints deul fin du XX{{e}} sièke<ref>{{en}} Naxos Classical Music Spotlight podcast: Philip Glass Heroes Symphony</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{en}} [http://nymag.com/news/features/influentials/16903/ New York News and Features: The Influentials: Classical and Dance]</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{en}} [http://www.guardian.co.uk/Archive/Article/0,4273,4306156,00.html Guardian Unlimited: When less means more]</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{en}} [http://www.rhapsody.com/philipglass Rhapsody Online artist profile of Philip Glass]</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{fr}} [http://www.andante.com/article/article.cfm?id=17307 Andante online: A Composer's Century]</ref>. 
